urn to certain event and try to assess them in a new wai but thei should be assess as thei were at the time thei happen in februari 1917 the czar renounc the throne virtual voluntarili and the peopl receiv thi posit thei did not take to the street chant the slogan restor the autocraci on the contrari thei rejoic thei saw it as a revolut a peac quiet revolut a wai of align themselv with the state of europ that had also renounc their monarchi it wa a festiv for russia but time pass and now we think it wa more or less a tragedi histori march on it cannot be deflect or turn back you cannot keep reassess thing it must be realiz that clearli there ar two wai of assess everi phenomenon czar peter i wa great by virtu of hi victori but there were also mani sacrific on the altar of those victori becaus the too rapid european of russia had not onli posit but also neg consequ the destruct of the tradit of the patriarch russian famili that too had neg consequ drunken and absente certainli date from those dai from peter s time and smoke and other featur of european life so in addit to civil europ also brought to russia a corrupt element sai under stalin s regim we were a close countri that wa also posit to some extent for instanc with respect to the fact that we were almost complet free of vener diseas and moral in gener wa at a high level i wa at school from 1953 to 1964 and all the girl in our class were virgin and if ani girl happen to give us reason to think that she had alreadi embark on a sex life thi wa seen in veri neg term at the ag of 17 or 18 we gui were pure with a well balanc mental we did not have a drug addict we did not sniff anyth and as for alcohol just a littl at home with our parent on festiv dai and nobodi made ani comment to us about whether we drank a lot or a littl it did not even enter our head even the word restaur wa consid not quit nice and peopl who went to such place were certainli seen as peopl with extrem bad charact of cours thi wa a provinci outl